metadata.name: I Miss My Friend (Goat Horn #1)
metadata.description:
This song is dedicated to those who are no longer with us on our journey on this astral plane. Living or passed on... Thank you for being. 

cor·nu·co·pi·a

/ ˌkôrn(y)əˈkōpēə / (noun)

1. a symbol of plenty consisting of a goat's horn overflowing with flowers, fruit, and corn.

2. an ornamental container shaped like a goat's horn.
an abundant supply of good things of a specified kind.
"the festival offers a cornucopia of pleasures"
